sequenceDiagram
    participant KFTO as Kubeflow Training<br/>Operator
    participant AccLaunch as accelerate_launch.py<br/>Container Entry Point
    participant SFT as sft_trainer.py<br/>Training Orchestration
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PVCIn as PVC /data/input<br/>Filesystem
    participant GPU as GPU (CUDA)<br/>PCIe/NVLink
    participant Workers as FSDP Workers<br/>29500/TCP plaintext
    participant PVCOut as PVC /data/output<br/>Filesystem
    participant Tracker as MLflow/Aim/ClearML<br/>HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over KFTO,Tracker: Flow 1: Training Job Execution

    KFTO->>AccLaunch: Create PyTorchJob Pod<br/>Kubernetes API (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
    activate AccLaunch

    AccLaunch->>AccLaunch: Parse JSON config<br/>(SFT_TRAINER_CONFIG_JSON_PATH)<br/>Auto-detect GPU count

    AccLaunch->>HFHub: Download model & tokenizer<br/>HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
    HFHub-->>AccLaunch: Model weights & tokenizer files

    AccLaunch->>SFT: Launch training (in-process)
    activate SFT

    SFT->>PVCIn: Load training dataset<br/>Filesystem (POSIX permissions)
    PVCIn-->>SFT: Training data (JSON/JSONL/Parquet/Arrow)

    SFT->>SFT: Data preprocessing<br/>Tokenization, chat templates<br/>Vision data collation

    SFT->>GPU: Forward/backward pass<br/>PCIe/NVLink
    GPU-->>SFT: Gradients

    SFT->>Workers: FSDP gradient synchronization<br/>29500/TCP (c10d static rendezvous)<br/>Encryption: plaintext<br/>Auth: None
    Workers-->>SFT: Synchronized gradients

    loop Training Loop (epochs)
        SFT->>GPU: Forward/backward pass
        GPU-->>SFT: Gradients
        SFT->>Workers: Gradient sync (FSDP)
        Workers-->>SFT: Synchronized gradients
        SFT->>SFT: Trainer Controller<br/>Rule evaluation (simpleeval)<br/>Early stopping check

        opt Experiment Tracking
            SFT->>Tracker: Log metrics (loss, lr, epoch)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (configurable)<br/>Auth: URI/API key
        end
    end

    SFT->>PVCOut: Save model checkpoint<br/>Filesystem (POSIX permissions)<br/>safetensors format
    PVCOut-->>SFT: Write confirmation

    deactivate SFT

    Note over AccLaunch,PVCOut: Flow 2: vLLM Adapter Post-Processing

    AccLaunch->>PVCOut: Read adapter_model.safetensors<br/>from checkpoint directory
    PVCOut-->>AccLaunch: LoRA adapter weights

    AccLaunch->>AccLaunch: post_process_vLLM_adapters<br/>Extract new embeddings

    AccLaunch->>PVCOut: Write new_embeddings.safetensors<br/>Write .complete sentinel file

    deactivate AccLaunch
